- "Quokka?"
- Yes, it's Quokka.

236
00:07:10,850 --> 00:07:11,850
- Oh, Quokka?
- Oh, I get it.

237
00:07:11,851 --> 00:07:13,449
- The animal living in Australia?
- Correct.

238
00:07:13,450 --> 00:07:15,149
Quokkas are an endangered species.

239
00:07:15,150 --> 00:07:17,819
My fans started calling me "Quokka," saying I looked like a quokka...

240
00:07:17,820 --> 00:07:19,389
when I smile. They found my smile cute.

241
00:07:19,390 --> 00:07:21,419
- Quokkas like humans so much.
- They smile with their eyes.

242
00:07:21,420 --> 00:07:22,429
- Exactly.
- It's like a squirrel...

243
00:07:22,430 --> 00:07:24,910
Shin Young, show us how they look. Try to imitate their faces.

244
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:26,959
Oh, I get it.

245
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:29,270
- I get it now.
- I want to see a quokka.

246
00:07:29,770 --> 00:07:31,269
- It must look so cute.
- Yes, it does.

247
00:07:31,270 --> 00:07:33,299
- It looks like it's smiling.
- Oh, I see.

248
00:07:33,300 --> 00:07:34,999
- A quokka looks like it's smiling.
- It has a smiling face.

249
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:37,609
Just imagine a big squirrel.

250
00:07:37,610 --> 00:07:38,610
- Jang Hoon.
- Yes?

251
00:07:39,010 --> 00:07:40,939
Why did you use the word "big" when I imitated a quokka?

252
00:07:40,940 --> 00:07:42,980
That's not what I meant. I just described a quokka.

253
00:07:43,510 --> 00:07:44,879
- A quokka is like a big squirrel.
- You meant a quokka?

254
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:45,880
- Okay.
- Why...

255
00:07:45,881 --> 00:07:48,019
- Sorry. I feel inferior.
- Why do you feel inferior?

256
00:07:48,020 --> 00:07:49,460
Okay. That's my inferiority complex.

257
00:07:49,550 --> 00:07:51,619
- I admit it.
- You got it after your comeback.

258
00:07:51,620 --> 00:07:53,419
- Sorry.
- I don't really think...

259
00:07:53,420 --> 00:07:54,959
of others when I speak.

260
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:56,759
- Soyou's nickname is...
- I think so.

261
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:58,929
- Makes sense. It's Voice Queen.
- What is it?

262
00:07:58,930 --> 00:08:01,399
I wrote that because you described me that way...

263
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:02,499
- Voice Queen?
- whenever I came here.

264
00:08:02,500 --> 00:08:03,799
You always called me "Voice Queen."

265
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:05,099
- Voice Queen. Right.
- That's true.

266
00:08:05,100 --> 00:08:07,339
I used to have many other nicknames including Bbangkku Ttongkku.

267
00:08:07,340 --> 00:08:08,839
- Oh, right. Bbangkku Ttongkku.
- Oh, Bbangkku Ttongkku.

268
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:10,810
I used to be called Chun Myung Hoon as well.

269
