271
00:08:15,010 --> 00:08:16,149
In which I look like him...

272
00:08:16,150 --> 00:08:18,779
because I'm squinting because of the sunlight.

273
00:08:18,780 --> 00:08:21,179
- You looked like him.
- People said I looked like him.

274
00:08:21,180 --> 00:08:24,790
Hold on. Hanbin, you don't know Chun Myung Hoon, do you?

275
00:08:25,390 --> 00:08:26,390
I've heard his name.

276
00:08:27,290 --> 00:08:29,589
This is how huge the generation gap is between them.

277
00:08:29,590 --> 00:08:30,959
The 2.5th and the 5th generations are different.

278
00:08:30,960 --> 00:08:32,159
- He's a member of NRG.
- I've heard a lot about him.

279
00:08:32,160 --> 00:08:33,160
- A member of NRG.
- He's a Hong Kong singer.

280
00:08:33,161 --> 00:08:34,359
- He wouldn't know NRG.
- Look at his face.

281
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:36,200
(I can do it)

282
00:08:36,430 --> 00:08:38,376
- Yes! I don't know that song.
- Do you know this song?

283
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:39,770
But I know Roo'Ra.

284
00:08:40,800 --> 00:08:42,409
- He transcends generations.
- As a matter of fact...

285
00:08:42,410 --> 00:08:44,409
There have been a lot of incidents involving Roo'Ra.

286
00:08:44,410 --> 00:08:45,410
Exactly.

287
00:08:45,940 --> 00:08:47,609
- He must've watched the news.
- He...

288
00:08:47,610 --> 00:08:48,610
- He knows Roo'Ra.
- Then...

289
00:08:48,611 --> 00:08:50,379
I know Roo'Ra because I watch this show often.

290
00:08:50,380 --> 00:08:52,079
- Hanbin, do you know Buzz?
- Oh, I see.

291
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,150
Of course, I know Buzz.

292
00:08:53,850 --> 00:08:54,850
(Thorn)

293
