294
00:08:58,090 --> 00:09:00,859
Kyung Hoon, how on earth did you act while singing as Buzz?

295
00:09:00,860 --> 00:09:01,860
I don't know.

296
00:09:02,860 --> 00:09:04,789
- I didn't mean to offend you.
- None taken.

297
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:07,036
(He suddenly remembers the days when he mocked Kyung Hoon.)

298
00:09:07,060 --> 00:09:08,969
- It's all my fault.
- Thorn.

299
00:09:08,970 --> 00:09:10,899
- But...
- Let's move on.

300
00:09:10,900 --> 00:09:13,099
- Sandeul's nickname is...
- Who's up next?

301
00:09:13,100 --> 00:09:14,739
Master Singer Duck.

302
00:09:14,740 --> 00:09:16,309
- "Master Singer Duck?"
- "Master Singer Duck."

303
00:09:16,310 --> 00:09:17,910
My nickname has always been "Duck..."

304
00:09:18,210 --> 00:09:20,279
because I have a protruding mouth.

305
00:09:20,280 --> 00:09:22,479
My fans gave me the nickname "Duck."

306
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:25,249
You have a protruding mouth? It's like holding a candle to the sun.

307
00:09:25,250 --> 00:09:27,649
But I really surprised myself...

308
00:09:27,650 --> 00:09:28,950
when I was on another show.

309
00:09:29,190 --> 00:09:32,020
We played this game where we had to guess a person...

310
00:09:32,190 --> 00:09:34,670
- only by looking at his mouth.
- You had to guess who it was?

311
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:37,929
One of the photos made me think, "This person's life must be tough."

312
00:09:37,930 --> 00:09:38,999
And it turned out to be my photo.

313
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:40,329
- Oh, my.
- Did you pick that photo?

314
00:09:40,330 --> 00:09:41,829
