- Shin Young,

403
00:12:45,050 --> 00:12:46,726
how long did it take you to regain the weight you lost?

404
00:12:46,750 --> 00:12:48,180
It took me only six weeks.

405
00:12:49,150 --> 00:12:50,919
- So it takes 6 months...
- It takes 6 months to lose weight,

406
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:53,059
- but it comes back in six weeks.
- It's hard to lose weight.

407
00:12:53,060 --> 00:12:55,859
- How much weight did you lose?
- It took Shin Young ten years.

408
00:12:55,860 --> 00:12:59,660
I weighed 88kg when I started losing weight.

409
00:12:59,860 --> 00:13:01,500
And my weight dropped to 44kg.

410
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:03,729
- You lost an entire person.
- You lost the weight of a person.

411
00:13:03,730 --> 00:13:05,999
I lost the weight of a whole person. Maybe a fifth grader.

412
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:07,869
Then did you regain the weight...

413
00:13:07,870 --> 00:13:09,286
How did you feel when you lost the weight?

414
00:13:09,310 --> 00:13:10,509
- When I was slimmer, - Yes.

415
00:13:10,510 --> 00:13:13,040
- the world felt like sand.
- Exactly.

416
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:14,579
- I became very sensitive.
- Right. That happens.

417
00:13:14,580 --> 00:13:17,880
I reacted in a prickly way to trivial things.

418
00:13:18,010 --> 00:13:19,779
- I was quite sensitive.
- Shin Young.

419
00:13:19,780 --> 00:13:22,820
Are you saying you gained over 40kg in only 6 weeks?

420
00:13:23,050 --> 00:13:26,090
No. I don't weigh 88kg now.

421
00:13:27,060 --> 00:13:29,029
- She's angry.
- I'm sorry.

422
00:13:29,030 --> 00:13:31,059
- That's okay.
- I'm sorry.

423
00:13:31,060 --> 00:13:32,189
It's my inferiority complex.

424
00:13:32,190 --> 00:13:33,899
- Right.
- I'm sorry.

425
00:13:33,900 --> 00:13:36,930
She would've gotten furious if she weighed 44kg.

426
00:13:37,270 --> 00:13:39,540
- That's crazy. I'm sorry.
- I would've stepped forward.

427
00:13:40,070 --> 00:13:41,646
- I would've stepped forward.
- I have a question.

428
00:13:41,670 --> 00:13:44,509
Soyou is known as the queen of collaboration.

429
00:13:44,510 --> 00:13:45,779
- That's right.
- Yes.

430
00:13:45,780 --> 00:13:47,810
Did some people think you used a ghost singer?

431
00:13:49,050 --> 00:13:51,579
"Officially Missing You, Too" was the first song I featured on,

432
00:13:51,580 --> 00:13:53,080
and when the song came out,

433
00:13:53,850 --> 00:13:55,650
many people thought it wasn't my voice.

434
00:13:56,190 --> 00:13:57,849
They thought someone else had recorded the song,

435
00:13:57,850 --> 00:13:59,690
and that I was claiming the song as my own.

436
00:14:00,190 --> 00:14:02,389
It's because I sang SISTAR's songs with a clear, solid voice...

437
00:14:02,390 --> 00:14:05,190
- instead of a raspy voice.
- Right.

438
00:14:05,460 --> 00:14:07,699
Many people shared that suspicion.

439
00:14:07,700 --> 00:14:10,229
- Many I knew asked me about it.
- Right.

440
00:14:10,230 --> 00:14:12,230
Five, six, seven, eight.

441
00:14:26,580 --> 00:14:27,860
She sounds completely different.

442
00:14:29,950 --> 00:14:31,749
- Here...
- It really is her voice.

443
00:14:31,750 --> 00:14:32,989
(Her live performance was so great that it put the rumor to rest.)

444
00:14:32,990 --> 00:14:34,789
- She sang with her own voice, yes?
- That was so good.

445
00:14:34,790 --> 00:14:36,859
Whenever I hear Ho Dong speak in dialect...

446
00:14:36,860 --> 00:14:39,529
- Sang Gook is popular these days.
- That's right.

447
00:14:39,530 --> 00:14:41,900
He sounds like he's trying to copy Yang Sang Gook.

448
00:14:43,430 --> 00:14:44,830
- Is he imitating Sang Gook?
- Hey!

449
00:14:45,970 --> 00:14:47,169
- Is he imitating Sang Gook?
- Hey!

450
00:14:47,170 --> 00:14:49,539
- I never imagined...
- That brat is a fake.

451
00:14:49,540 --> 00:14:51,169
- He called Sang Gook a fake.
- Sang Gook is very popular, so...

452
00:14:51,170 --> 00:14:52,539
- "He's a fake."
- That brat is...

453
00:14:52,540 --> 00:14:54,060
Why does he sound like he's faking it?

454
00:14:54,210 --> 00:14:57,910
(That brat talks like he's from Seoul now.)

455
00:14:58,180 --> 00:15:01,219
- In Ho Dong's life...
- He just babbles on in dialect.

456
00:15:01,220 --> 00:15:02,749
Aren't you benchmarking Yang Sang Gook?

457
00:15:02,750 --> 00:15:03,849
- Benchmarking?
- Right.

458
00:15:03,850 --> 00:15:05,149
I said he was a fake.

459
00:15:05,150 --> 00:15:07,319
- Maybe Sang Gook is his role model.
- Exactly.

460
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:08,789
My gosh. I'm speechless.

461
00:15:08,790 --> 00:15:10,089
Aren't you going to release a new song soon?

462
00:15:10,090 --> 00:15:11,959
- I will release a new song soon.
- Do you sing with another man?

463
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:14,329
- I'm going solo this time.
- I see.

464
00:15:14,330 --> 00:15:15,769
So, you are not featuring on others' song?

465
00:15:15,770 --> 00:15:17,869
